                            time(datetime="2016-01-07") Thursday, 7 January 2016
                    li.media
                        .media-left
                            a(href="http://blog.backfeed.cc/backfeeds-economic-model-for-an-decentralized-age/", target="_blank")
                                img.media-object(src="/assets/images/blog-post-2.jpg", alt="Post featured image")
                        .media-body
                            h4.media-heading
                                a(href="http://blog.backfeed.cc/backfeeds-economic-model-for-an-decentralized-age/", target="_blank") Backfeeds' economic model for an decentralized age
